descriptionHtml:
🏥 [1700+ clinics in South Korea]
Find the most suitable clinic for you on GangnamUnni where most number of Korean clinics are registered.

👨‍⚕️ [Real doctors to answer your question]
Share your questions or concerns on GangnamUnni Forum. GangnamUnni users and doctors will pitch in to help, 24/7.

✍🏻 [100k Verified Reviews]
Users who completed clinic consultation through GangnamUnni, can leave verified reviews. Check out the verified reviews before choosing a clinic or treatment.

🎁 [Free Recovery Care Package after surgery]
Worried about recovery? GangnamUnni users who book clinic visit though the app and complete a surgery are eligible for Free Care Package worth 150k KRW :D

👍 [Treatment Discount Events]
Choose from over 3,000 treatments on special price. Compare how much your treatment will cost at each clinic and learn the pros and cons from home.

*Required App Permission
- Call : Make calls to clinic to set up appointment
- Save : Save or upload photos

*Elective App Permission
- Camera : Upload photos on posts
(You can use the app without granting elective app permission)

You may change your App Permission setting by going to [Setting > Application > GangnamUnni > Permission] menu. If your OS version is lower than Android 6.0, you may need to upgrade to a recent version in order to be able to change each setting.

*Inquiries about the App
Please contact our Customer Center (http://gangnamunni.channel.io) should you have any questions about the app or are facing issues.
(We are unable to follow up on your questions submitted on PlayStore Review due to lack of contact info and issue details.)

title: GangnamUnni - Cosmetic Surgery & Reviews

creator: 강남언니
descriptionHtml:
🏥 [1800+ clinics in South Korea]
Find the most suitable clinic for you on GangnamUnni where most number of Korean clinics are registered.

👨‍⚕️ [Real doctors to answer your question]
Share your questions or concerns on GangnamUnni Forum. GangnamUnni users and doctors will pitch in to help, 24/7.

✍🏻 [250k Verified Reviews]
Users who completed clinic consultation through GangnamUnni, can leave verified reviews. Check out the verified reviews before choosing a clinic or treatment.

🎁 [Free Recovery Care Package after surgery]
Worried about recovery? GangnamUnni users who book clinic visit though the app and complete a surgery are eligible for Free Care Package worth 120k KRW :D

👍 [Treatment Discount Events]
Choose from over 3,000 treatments on special price. Compare how much your treatment will cost at each clinic and learn the pros and cons from home.

*Required App Permission
- Call : Make calls to clinic to set up appointment
- Save : Save or upload photos

*Elective App Permission
- Camera : Upload photos on posts
(You can use the app without granting elective app permission)

You may change your App Permission setting by going to [Setting > Application > GangnamUnni > Permission] menu. If your OS version is lower than Android 6.0, you may need to upgrade to a recent version in order to be able to change each setting.

*Inquiries about the App
Please contact our Customer Center (http://gangnamunni.channel.io) should you have any questions about the app or are facing issues.
(We are unable to follow up on your questions submitted on PlayStore Review due to lack of contact info and issue details.)

creator: 강남언니
descriptionHtml:
🏥 [1 out of 3 entire plastic surgery clinics chose GangnamUnni]
You can choose a clinic through GangnamUnni the app that provides an outstanding number of clinical information. Carefully compare the reviews of each clinics before your first visit to the clinic!

🌟 [Special pricing events are updated every month!]
Choose a special-priced clinical events in GangnamUnni.

✍🏻 [A real review proved with receipts]
Check 650000 review and choose a plastic surgical & clinical treatment that suits for you.

🎁 [GangnamUnni provides a swelling management package when you write a surgery review]
GangnamUnni provides a 100,000 won worth swelling management package when you received a surgery through GangnamUnni and leave a review. No worries on downtime!

👨‍⚕️[Continuous users chats and doctors’ response]
Users and doctors will answer your questions within 24 hours

💎[GangnamUnni provides points when you sign up or write a review!]
Get 5000 sign up points, and get more points for writing reviews! (You can use the points when you purchase a treatment.

*Necessary authorization access
- Call : Used to make a phone call to contact clinics
- Save : Used to save and upload photos

* optional authorization access
- Camera : Used to upload photos on review/ chats
[Settings > GangnamUnni > Authorization to GangnamUnni] You can agree/withdraw the authorization using the path above.
GangnamUnni’s authorization access works on versions above AOS 6.0. If the version you are using is below 6.0, we highly recommend to update the version as you cannot selectively agree on the authorization access.


*Contacts for questions
Please contact the customer service if you have any questions or problems.(http://gangnamunni.channel.io)
*It is difficult to answer questions uploaded as a review.

title: GangnamUnni - Medical beauty

creator: 강남언니
descriptionHtml:
🏥 [1 out of 3 entire plastic surgery clinics chose GangnamUnni]
You can choose a clinic through GangnamUnni the app that provides an outstanding number of clinical information. Carefully compare the reviews of each clinics before your first visit to the clinic!

🌟 [Special pricing events are updated every month!]
Choose a special-priced clinical events in GangnamUnni.

✍🏻 [A real review proved with receipts]
Check 650000 review and choose a plastic surgical & clinical treatment that suits for you.

🎁 [GangnamUnni provides a swelling management package when you write a surgery review]
GangnamUnni provides a 100,000 won worth swelling management package when you received a surgery through GangnamUnni and leave a review. No worries on downtime!

👨‍⚕️[Continuous users chats and doctors’ response]
Users and doctors will answer your questions within 24 hours

💎[GangnamUnni provides points when you sign up or write a review!]
Get 5000 sign up points, and get more points for writing reviews! (You can use the points when you purchase a treatment.

*Necessary authorization access
- Call : Used to make a phone call to contact clinics
- Save : Used to save and upload photos

* optional authorization access
- Camera : Used to upload photos on review/ chats
[Settings > GangnamUnni > Authorization to GangnamUnni] You can agree/withdraw the authorization using the path above.
GangnamUnni’s authorization access works on versions above AOS 6.0. If the version you are using is below 6.0, we highly recommend to update the version as you cannot selectively agree on the authorization access.


*Contacts for questions
Please contact the customer service if you have any questions or problems.(http://gangnamunni.channel.io)
*It is difficult to answer questions uploaded as a review.
